{"tid":811411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似比補習中介呃撚左錢⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-09-08T18:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T09:54:12.000Z","uid":173592,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"49b6c13cc544c6eb41996bbf8b11482aacca3f13","tid":811411,"uid":173592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:51:19.000Z","msg":"話說8月接左個上門補習，補左2堂個家長話佢成家去旅行，開左學再約時間補，到左早2日我問佢會唔會繼續補，個家長話仲觀察緊，唔洗留時間比佢⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n屌 觀乜撚察！唔補點撚觀呀！我頭2堂啲學費都係中介收⋯⋯我一堂錢都未收過呀仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n好驚係個家長同中介夾埋一齊呃錢⋯⋯之前用其他中介都冇事，呢個第一次用就出事⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人都試過類似嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404097b74a2227c33346ace0878632ddcbad0f35","tid":811411,"uid":120542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:52:10.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6b23bbe8915bd070be972927f79803126bcb58","tid":811411,"uid":38383,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:53:26.000Z","msg":"聽過好多次 放心 你一定係比中介呃撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfa966df6e89526bc34ffcd55ebd093003b975b","tid":811411,"uid":173592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"404097b74a2227c33346ace0878632ddcbad0f35","tid":811411,"uid":120542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:52:10.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T19:04:24.000Z","msg":"K_ _ _  Tutor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2240a7549bc5ef68dedcc89a6e8fb8202ed761","tid":811411,"uid":26157,"like":